criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Best corrected visual acuity of 20/25 in both eyes at distance and near;

          -  Willingness to wear eyeglasses or contact lenses to correct refractive error, if
             necessary;

          -  500" random dot stereopsis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Amblyopia (lazy eye);

          -  Eye disease
